data.description: Country living at its finest! This unrestricted 5 acre property nestled on the outskirts of Dripping Springs offers incredible sunset views, poolside fun, room for horses and so much more. The 1967sqft home features a freshly painted 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a detached 2 car garage+bonus room connected by a breezeway all overlooking the pool. A well equipped outdoor kitchen connected to the garage bonus room includes everything you need for entertaining. Private sliding glass door access from the owners suite to the new hot tub is complimented by a view of the backyard and oak covered acreage. Several outbuildings include horse stalls w/ tack room, storage shed, well house and dedicated/covered RV parking. Cross fencing is already in place to create a generous yard, space for the horses and several acres on the back side of the property left for your imagination. LOTS of updates have been done: new roof, Generac system with dedicated propane tank, HVAC, water heater and SO MUCH MORE! Complete list attached in listing docs. Don't miss this move-in ready home with space to breathe deep and enjoy the Texas hill country.
